name: Shona Weeks
text: Such beautiful arrangements and unique items for the home. Year round items that are really gorgeous and look real!!!

name: Tim Elam
text: Wonderful selection of high-end designer handcrafted artificial flower arrangements, plants, trees, and coordinated accessories. The staff are extremely knowledgeable of today's interior design trends and are super friendly. The Showroom contains a large variety of products and is updated frequently. The Design Center offers a welcoming creative space for meetings, consultations, and collaborations. It's available by appointment only during normal showroom hours and is offered as a complimentary service to design professionals.
